
;配布奴隷の種族合わせ
@CHARA_MAKE_FIXED_SLAVE_TRIBE_QUESTION
#DIM TRIBE_RATIO
#DIM TRIBE_NUM

TRIBE_RATIO = 0
TRIBE_NUM = 0
PRINTFORML %CALLNAME%的种族【%CSTR:种族%】在游戏中设置的出现率为0。

;それぞれの割合を比べて一番高い種族
;同じだった場合は番号若いほう
;FLAG:候補割合／一般種族／人間→2600
FLAG_REF = 2600
FOR LOCAL,2600,2620
	IF TRIBE_RATIO < FLAG:LOCAL
		TRIBE_NUM = LOCAL
		TRIBE_RATIO = FLAG:LOCAL
	ENDIF
NEXT

;STR:人間→6510
TRIBE_NUM -= FLAG_REF
TRIBE_NUM += 6510
PRINTL
PRINTFORML 是否将%CALLNAME%的种族更改为出现率最高的【%STR:TRIBE_NUM%】？
PRINTFORMLC [ 0] 保留为【%CSTR:种族%】
PRINTFORML [ 1] 变为【%STR:TRIBE_NUM%】
INPUT
IF RESULT
	CSTR:种族 = %STR:TRIBE_NUM%
	CALL CHARA_MAKE_FIXED_SLAVE_TRIBE_TALENT
ENDIF



;種族での素質合わせ
@CHARA_MAKE_FIXED_SLAVE_TRIBE_TALENT

;この部分だけは全部合わせる
TALENT:动物耳朵 = 0
TALENT:尾巴 = 0
TALENT:两角 = 0
SELECTCASE CSTR:种族
CASE "犬耳族","猫耳族","兔耳族","狐耳族","狸耳族","妖狐"
	TALENT:动物耳朵 = 1
	TALENT:尾巴 = 1

CASE "牛角族","羊角族"
	TALENT:动物耳朵 = 1
	TALENT:尾巴 = 1
	TALENT:两角 = 1

CASE "龙人"
	TALENT:尾巴 = 1
	TALENT:两角 = 1
ENDSELECT
PRINTW 已根据更改后的种族调整【动物耳】【尾巴】【双角】素质。




